window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>In this epic conclusion to the first series in the Human Chronicles Saga, Adam Cain and his band of Human warriors are presented to the Supreme Leader of the Galaxy. With only minutes to live, Adam convinces the Juirean leader that Humans are not the enemy, but that both their races have been part of a diabolical plot for galactic domination orchestrated by the Klin. </p> <p>And yet just when the truth dawns on the Juireans, the planet Juir is attacked by Kracori forces, which leads to a whole new set of problems for Adam and his band of Human Super-Men. </p> <p>In a galaxy where Humans are the superior race, we find that with superior strength and fighting skills comes responsibility. Can the Humans rule the universe, or will they be replaced by the Kracori or the Klin? You might be surprised with the outcome....</p>"; 
